        "content": "<div class=\"article-content\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6\"><span class=\"tag-ai px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">AI技术</span><span class=\"text-gray-500\">2026-02-27</span></div><h1>生成式AI辅助游戏美术工作流</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-gray-300\">Stable Diffusion、Midjourney等工具正在革新美术管线。本文探讨AI生成纹理、概念艺术、以及如何在项目中合规使用生成式AI。</p><div class=\"tech-analysis-box\" style=\"border-color: #ff006e40;\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold\" style=\"color: #ff006e\">🔬 技术分析</span></div><p class=\"mb-0 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">生成式AI可以快速产出概念设计和纹理变体。技术工作流包括：使用ControlNet保持构图一致性、LoRA微调生成特定风格、以及DreamBooth训练角色一致性。法律和伦理考虑包括版权归属、训练数据授权、以及AI辅助vs AI生成的标注。</p></div><h2>🎯 核心技术</h2><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6\"><span class=\"tag-ai px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">Stable Diffusion</span><span class=\"tag-ai px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">ControlNet</span><span class=\"tag-ai px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">LoRA微调</span><span class=\"tag-ai px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">纹理生成</span><span class=\"tag-ai px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm\">概念艺术</span></div></div>",
